title: BunnyJOY Magnetic Letters and Numbers for Children, 106PCS Alphabet Fridge Magnets for Toddlers, Preschool Educational Toys, Spelling & Counting Learning Set, Magnetic Alphabet Set for Kids
features: 【ALL-IN-ONE LEARNING ADVENTURE】This 106-piece magnetic set is a colorful treasure chest for little learners, with 26 uppercase letters, 52 lowercase letters, 20 numbers, 6 symbols, and 2 surprise pieces. In five bold colors—green, blue, orange, red, and yellow—this set makes learning letters, numbers, spelling, and counting an exciting journey full of fun and discovery!

【IDEAL FOR EARLY LEARNING】This magnetic set is a fantastic way to kickstart early education! Whether used at home or in the classroom, it’s ideal for helping children master spelling, counting, color recognition, and hand-eye coordination. It’s a must-have for any budding learner, making education feel like an adventure.

【EASY STORAGE, QUICK CLEANUP】No more searching for missing pieces! The kit comes with a handy drawstring bag that keeps everything neatly stowed away. When playtime is over, just gather up the magnets, toss them in the bag, and you're good to go—organization made simple.

【SIZED FOR LITTLE HANDS】Crafted from lightweight, smooth plastic, these magnets are made for small hands to easily grasp and explore. Thanks to their strong magnetic backing, they stick securely to any metal surface—be it a fridge, a magnetic board, or even a dishwasher—opening the door to hands-on learning fun.

【INTERACTIVE LEARNING, ENDLESS FUN】Encouraging kids to actively engage with letters, numbers, and colors, this set makes learning feel like play. It’s a great way for children to practice spelling, explore math concepts, and ignite their creativity, all while having a blast, whether they’re learning solo or playing with friends.
